content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #91377 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
Per Noah's comment as well as my own, I think this is expected behavior. I suggest we remove I-prioritize and regression-from-stable-to-stable and add C-discussion.
agreed. Interesting, I've rarely used that c-discussion. Since it's already labeled T-lang, I'll probably also add I-lang-nominate, it should have the effect of slipping this issue in their agenda
